cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.HC 

This paper deals with the task of kinship verification using facial images. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper proposes a novel approach for feature representation using deep learning, which falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also utilizes unsupervised learning techniques, which is a common theme in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The proposed approach is evaluated on multiple datasets, which falls under the category of cs.MM (Multimedia). Finally, the paper also conducts a human study to understand the capabilities of the human mind, which falls under the category of cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction).
